# Package Conventions

- Add file headers per .context/RULES.md (@file, @summary, @exports, @invariants)
- Export via package index.ts; run `pnpm validate-exports` after changes
- @repo/ui: React is peerDependency, not direct
- Tests: Node env for lib/actions; jsdom for components (jest-axe, @testing-library/react)
- ESLint 9 flat config (eslint.config.mjs); extend @repo/eslint-config
